features: [Storage, 2 Layers] Keep all your jewelry organized in this jewelry box—small pieces of jewelry go in the various slots of the top layer, and big jewelry goes in the bottom drawer

[Clear Glass Lid] The see-through glass lid of this jewelry organizer allows you to see and find your favorite jewels at a glance while protecting them from dust, keeping your jewelry ready to wear and clean

[Chic & Durable] Elegant white and gold colors, shiny metal handles, soft velvet lining, neat stitching, quality PU, and sturdy MDF—all these elements combined make this jewelry case stylish and durable enough for your ever-growing jewelry collection
[Perfect Gift Idea] Gift this original design jewelry box to your loved ones for their birthday or anniversary to surprise them! Or, treat yourself to this fancy jewelry box—you deserve it!
[Versatile Use] This modern jewelry holder looks nice whether displayed on the dresser of your bedroom or your cloakroom to organize your pins, necklaces, rings, bracelets, and other accessories

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Look no where else!
reviews.reviewText: I recently got the this Jewelry Box, and it has effortlessly become a staple on my dresser. Here are a few things I absolutely love about it:- Sophisticated Appearance: The design is truly eye-catching. The combination of graphite black and silver gives it a modern and elegant touch that complements my room decor.- Value for Money: Given its high-quality build and finish, the price point is more than reasonable. It's not often that you find such quality at this price.- Spacious and Versatile: The box is deceptively spacious. With multi compartments tailored for various types of jewelry, organization has become a breeze. The added bonus of two drawers, each of a different size, ensures that both my chunkier and more delicate pieces have a safe home.- Perfect for Dresser Display: Its size and design make it perfect to sit atop a dresser. The glass lid is not just functional but adds to its aesthetic appeal, allowing a sneak peek into the treasures inside.All in all, this jewelry box by SONGMICS is a gem in itself. Whether you're looking for something functional, aesthetically pleasing, or both, this ticks all the boxes. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Like everyone else, I'm very impressed by these jewelry boxes. I ordered the one with no drawers as well as the 2 drawer one. They are beautifully put together. Very Pottery Barn looking (and maybe this is the pb supplier, idk). The drawer pulls all the way out, so you get more space than you think in that section. Make sure to look at the dimensions. It was a little smaller than I was expecting. Very perfect!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Attractive and organized
reviews.reviewText: Jewelry box may seem a bit overpriced but it had plenty of organization and the exterior material looks well put together. I would have liked to see one of the drawers with another divider or two but it still gets the job done. It easily held 15 bracelets, 12 pairs of earrings, 3 watches, and 10 necklaces. Nothing was bulky but I still have room for more earrings and plenty of ring space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love it! It's both functional and aesthetically pleasing. Looks great on my dresser and it has lots of room for jewelry. It's well made and will probably last me a long time. Definitely a good purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice color and attractive jewelry box, looks more expensive than it is
reviews.reviewText: I took one star off because a flimsy ribbon holds the lid up on either side; I wish something more sturdy connected the box to its lid. Other than that, I'm happy with this purchase and was able to use it to organize my bureau and clear out some of the clutter.

reviews.reviewTitle: Muy bonito, se ve elegante y bien hecho.
reviews.reviewText: Lo entregué como regalo de navidad, se veia muy bonito, la calidad de la construccion se ve buena y resistente, llego en perfectas condiciones, los colores son tal cual se ven en las fotos. Me lo imaginaba un poco mas grande de tamaño pero tiene buena cantidad de espacio para guardar.
Lo regalé en Navidad y le gustó mucho a la persona que se lo di. Él alajero se veía muy bonito y de buena calidad.
